%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7Su3B4.png&h=5b1affde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myvsQg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyvsQg4.png&h=ed8179a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7J93B5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7J93B5.png&h=74055c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衛衣+牛仔褲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFmfZau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFmfZau.png&h=85cd4ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵唔到好多靚圖 粗粗地用住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />save得太快起晒格"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"大致認同春夏裝<br />\n基本上黑白灰深藍呀呢啲純色t就冇死<br />\n怕入冷氣地方凍就加件淨色裇衫<br />\n(格仔裇衫要小心揀)<br />\n<br />\n成個夏天都著長褲會好熱<br />\n下身我覺得可以短啲既牛仔褲 大約到膝頭<br />\n都係黑色深藍淺藍色 同純色t基本上任搭<br />\n鞋就自便 唔好太浮誇既色大概都可以<br />\n保險就白色鞋 鞋型低筒既 普通sneakers 或者vans嗰類(首選有鞋帶既款) 百搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冬天既話以下係我覺得保險既<br />\n有啲對鞋係皮鞋既我覺得著波鞋安全啲<br />\n波鞋加唔加長襪就可以慢慢<br />\n因為咩色長襪都要小心<br />\n建議唔好亂試 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwVpgb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwVpgb6.png&h=e247f7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrBzDqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrBzDqx.png&h=8419103f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZt6uxi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZt6uxi.png&h=9e99c56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要係個感覺係乾淨 袋既話我覺得都係簡單背囊 或者唔帶袋 <br />\n<br />\n我心目中咁樣既穿搭應該唔會太差<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebcb8571dbcce90705a8542b6694f0a458a94ae","tid":1307163,"uid":278042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c105cb48b221f5154fc09e11f5fd785daceabc","tid":1307163,"uid":138357,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cc6ac0e53b3194c93f1a5fe0a8daef